AIS in the News

AIS academic staff are the most active in the University in reaching out to the local and international media through interviews and opinion pieces about key issues in Asian and International affairs. AIS staff's media Knowledge transfer is also featured on the CityU NewsCentre and Knowledge Transfer page of the College of Liberal Arts and Social Sciences.
